{"id":289516,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/【网络民议】习近平微服私访亲自在北京打的/","date":"2013-04-18T02:55:49Z","modified":"2013-04-18T06:47:08Z","title":"【网络民议】习近平“微服私访”亲自在北京打的","content":"<p><strong>据大公报报道，3月1日晚，北京出租司机郭立新拉到了一位不平常的乘客，在途中他问道：“就没人说您长得像某个人？没人说您像习总书记？”对方听了乐了一下就说：&#8221;你是头一个把我认出来的司机。&#8221;郭立新说，他请习近平写下“一帆风顺”四个字。</strong></p>\n\n\t\t<style type='text/css'>\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 {\n\t\t\t\tmargin: auto;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-item {\n\t\t\t\tfloat: left;\n\t\t\t\tmargin-top: 10px;\n\t\t\t\ttext-align: center;\n\t\t\t\twidth: 33%;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 img {\n\t\t\t\tborder: 2px solid #cfcfcf;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-caption {\n\t\t\t\tmargin-left: 0;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t/* see gallery_shortcode() in wp-includes/media.php */\n\t\t</style>\n\t\t<div id='gallery-1' class='gallery galleryid-289516 gallery-columns-3 gallery-size-thumbnail'><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/%e3%80%90%e7%bd%91%e7%bb%9c%e6%b0%91%e8%ae%ae%e3%80%91%e4%b9%a0%e8%bf%91%e5%b9%b3%e5%be%ae%e6%9c%8d%e7%a7%81%e8%ae%bf%e4%ba%b2%e8%87%aa%e5%9c%a8%e5%8c%97%e4%ba%ac%e6%89%93%e7%9a%84/%e5%87%ba%e7%a7%9f/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/出租-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/出租-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/出租-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/%e3%80%90%e7%bd%91%e7%bb%9c%e6%b0%91%e8%ae%ae%e3%80%91%e4%b9%a0%e8%bf%91%e5%b9%b3%e5%be%ae%e6%9c%8d%e7%a7%81%e8%ae%bf%e4%ba%b2%e8%87%aa%e5%9c%a8%e5%8c%97%e4%ba%ac%e6%89%93%e7%9a%84/%e5%87%ba%e7%a7%9f2/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigi